# NOTE: src/content/forms/ is intentionally COMMITTED (not ignored).
# It is synced from ../qualireps-v2 by `npm run sync-content`, but the deploy
# build (Vercel) has no access to that sibling repo, so the synced fiches must
# be in version control for the build to succeed. Re-sync + commit when the app
# content changes.
